---
import BaseLayout from '../../layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
---

<BaseLayout
  title="Privacy Policy | Hushbay"
  description="Hushbay privacy policy: learn how we protect your data privacy."
  lang="en"
  alternateZh="https://sleepisland.org/privacy/"
  alternateEn="https://sleepisland.org/en/privacy/"
>
  <article class="max-w-3xl mx-auto px-4 py-16 text-[var(--color-text-secondary)]">
    <h1 class="text-3xl font-bold text-white text-center mb-10">Privacy Policy</h1>

    <p class="mb-4">Last updated: February 19, 2026</p>

    <p class="mb-6">Hushbay ("we") values your privacy. This policy explains how we collect, use, and protect your information.</p>

    <h2 class="text-xl font-bold text-white mt-8 mb-4">1. Information Collection</h2>
    <p class="mb-4">Hushbay collects the following information to provide our services:</p>
    <ul class="list-disc list-inside space-y-2 mb-6">
      <li><strong class="text-white">Sleep data:</strong> Sleep time, wake time, deep/light sleep stages. Stored locally on your device.</li>
      <li><strong class="text-white">Audio data:</strong> Audio clips recorded during snore detection, processed and stored locally only.</li>
      <li><strong class="text-white">Usage data:</strong> Anonymous app usage statistics used to improve the product experience.</li>
    </ul>

    <h2 class="text-xl font-bold text-white mt-8 mb-4">2. Data Usage</h2>
    <p class="mb-4">We only use your data for:</p>
    <ul class="list-disc list-inside space-y-2 mb-6">
      <li>Providing sleep analysis and snore detection services</li>
      <li>Generating personalized sleep recommendations</li>
      <li>Improving app performance and user experience</li>
    </ul>

    <h2 class="text-xl font-bold text-white mt-8 mb-4">3. Data Storage & Security</h2>
    <p class="mb-6">Your sleep data and audio recordings are stored locally on your device. We do not upload your personal health data to cloud servers. We use industry-standard security measures to protect data transmission.</p>

    <h2 class="text-xl font-bold text-white mt-8 mb-4">4. Third-Party Services</h2>
    <p class="mb-6">We do not use third-party advertising SDKs. We may use anonymous crash reporting services to improve app stability.</p>

    <h2 class="text-xl font-bold text-white mt-8 mb-4">5. Your Rights</h2>
    <p class="mb-6">You can delete all personal data within the app at any time. For assistance, contact <a href="mailto:contact@sleepisland.org" class="text-[var(--color-accent-light)] hover:underline">contact@sleepisland.org</a>.</p>

    <h2 class="text-xl font-bold text-white mt-8 mb-4">6. Contact Us</h2>
    <p>For privacy-related questions, please contact <a href="mailto:contact@sleepisland.org" class="text-[var(--color-accent-light)] hover:underline">contact@sleepisland.org</a>.</p>
  </article>
</BaseLayout>
